    <h1>Thread</h1>
    <p class="description">A series of <strong>connected social media posts</strong> published in sequence by one author — used to share long-form ideas, tell stories, or break down complex topics beyond a single post's character limit. Threads are the long-form format of short-form platforms.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
